{"tid":311004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台電視台老闆與女議員開房","createTime":"2017-07-06T08:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T10:25:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0419f1a6bd38d4af78157a540f29e905dbe78e99","tid":311004,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:57:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170706/20080517\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170706%2F20080517&d=3NzjFrGZfXEbbcbOPorIbF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=a762d86c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170706%2F20080517&h=48d4e2ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170706/20080517</a><br />\n<br />\n台電視台老闆與女議員開房<br />\n<br />\n11,853<br />\n <br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n台灣三立電視台董事長林崑海（63歲），昨被周刊踼爆，涉與年輕20年、同為綠營的高雄市女議員顏曉菁（43歲）開房！二人疑為避人耳目，從高雄市開45分鐘車程到台南市約會。有分析指，事件被曝光或有政治陰謀。<br />\n根據《鏡週刊》報道，林崑海上月23日傍晚被拍到，開平治房車載顏曉菁出遊，一路從高雄直奔台南，45分鐘後進了知名汽車旅館夏卡爾。二人待了大約1小時後，驅車前往中西區吃牛肉湯補充體力，接着又去土雞城採購兩大包食物，最後才由林送顏回家。據稱，林與顏開房同時，林妻張秀外出，去了搭高鐵。對於被拍到與女議員開房，林日前被記者質詢時一開始否認，但記者進一步表示掌握照片時，林瞬間結巴。<br />\n<br />\n被爆醜聞涉選舉鬥爭<br />\n有地方政界人士透露，林崑海與顏曉菁的戀情持續至少3年。至今未婚的顏原是民進黨內新潮流派，與陳菊同派系，但約兩年前，轉投靠林所屬的「海派」。由於明年舉行的下屆高雄市長選舉，海派支持的人選是立委陳其邁，而非陳菊較為相挺的另一位立委劉世芳。因而今次林顏開房事件被曝光，引發陰謀論。此外，另有傳因林崑海近日有意爭取民視經營權，因此被爆料。<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n華斥印度軍首度越境促撤離<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n吉林燃氣管道爆炸5死89傷"},{"pid":"518179233fa7fca1f8c89b3c9fa6135e83882c90","tid":311004,"uid":64949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:01:58.000Z","msg":"個呀嬋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc9750aa97677fcffcdaea89db6b1eac2f0aa05","tid":311004,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:09:25.000Z","msg":"唔係掛, 咁都食得落 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5700c732386e37730506a02502752b008ecc582","tid":311004,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:13:07.000Z","msg":"下一則<br />\n吉林燃氣管道爆炸5死89傷<br />\n<br />\n正評!!"},{"pid":"43cb8298abd6aef2322f3dc504a25acd32df37b2","tid":311004,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:13:20.000Z","msg":"台灣女人真係淫"},{"pid":"25916b3bb25b31fd7bfbec31606f486f1f614125","tid":311004,"uid":14135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:14:47.000Z","msg":"電視台老闆大把明星玩啦<br />\n走去搞個43歲阿嬋<br />\n係咩玩法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd66aa623963e5bc6a9022bcd402e50bdccc7b37","tid":311004,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:16:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電視台老闆大把明星玩啦<br />\n走去搞個43歲阿嬋<br />\n係咩玩法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n瘦版麥玲玲，顯然係真愛"},{"pid":"ec50d75f02b3df79d190c36f1200824f0f0ec262","tid":311004,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:19:08.000Z","msg":"幾大波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a7fd4bd03e8bb58834417a7a93d4bab534dbb6","tid":311004,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:22:46.000Z","msg":"講還講"},{"pid":"ba730bdddc4ea1026ab4ce601ab9396df12935cc","tid":311004,"uid":12757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:25:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講還講</blockquote><br />\n貼左再講 最多洗眼"}]}